Package: biofeedback-visualization
Type: Package
Title: Biofeedback Visualization Dashboard
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Tristin", "Yun", email = "tristinyun08@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive R Shiny application for analyzing the relationship between physiological data (heart rate variability) and audio performance data. Provides real-time visualization and analysis of how musical performance affects autonomic nervous system responses.
